(180, 3, 10, 'Mahadewi : You look very cheerful, Kaisar. What good news do you have? Kaisar : You know, I get a scholarship to study abroad, in the Australian National University, Canberra. My dreams come true. Mahadewi : Terrific. â¦! I\'m so happy to hear it.', 1, 'Let\'s celebrate it', 'You must be kidding', 'Oh come on', 'I am really flattered', 'Congratulations', 'E', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
