(182, 3, 12, 'Man : We have been waiting the bus for almost an hour. Woman : Yes, I suppose its route has changed. Man : As far as I know, it never passes through this road. Woman : What do you think we should do? Man : â¦', 1, 'I think we are supposed to change the bus', 'Why don\'t we should wait for the bus', 'I think it\'s better we take a taxi', 'How about asking the police?', 'Thank you very much', 'C', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
